This repo will contain a simple Android Application that should do the following:

1.  Always show the last known GeoLocation Data for the Phone
2.  Listen for changes in GeoLocation
3.  Allow the user to turn on GPS services from within the app
4.  Allow the user to turn off the GPS services from within the app
5.  Store a list of last X known locations.
6.  Allow user to enter a # of locations to store.  
